column17:
Product Description

Impart a vivacious charm to your room settings with this stylish and impeccably designed blanket. Made from polyester this blanket is detailed with floral motifs and offers adequate warmth to keep chilly nights at bay.A comfortable sleep is what this product promises. It is made from 100% polyester. The Colour and design of this blanket will surely brighten up your bedroom decor. The luster and sheen of the material will make this blanket an unforgettable one. Experience and feel the difference. Features: Hot Mink Single Bed Blanket Maximum Warmth Minimum Weight Soft and Cozy Easy to Store Weight: 900 gms. Fabric: 100% Polyester Ply: Single Ply Dimensions: 165 cms X 215 cms. Note : This is a 1 Piece Set only other accessories shown in the picture are for photography purpose only.
